title: Woman viciously assaulted in Auckland quarry
text:
Women of Influence BREAKING NEWS Injured woman wakes in a quarry to find a man standing over her with a bat in vicious attack... More soon Woman viciously assaulted in Auckland quarry Last updated 17:35, February 27 2017 NZ POLICE/SUPPLED 
Police are searching for the man pictured in this image. 
A woman woke up in an Auckland quarry, with injuries to her face and head, to find a man standing over her with a bat. 
Police said the victim called emergency services about 2.12am on Sunday morning. 
They are now asking for the public's help which may help them identify the man who was last seen with the woman before she was viciously assaulted. 
More to come.
